short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Dasseti extension is used for filling the web forms from dasseti application.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Dasseti extension can be used by registered users of the Dasseti application. This extension will assist users in completing web forms using Dasseti application data. The Registered users of Dasseti can insert the answers to web input controls from the Dasseti question answer bank. This will allow the user to easily utilize answers for our data bank instead of switching back to the application.
